Text: Re Agricultural Modeling SoftwareI wanted to follow up to confirm that we are still planning on a meeting for next Thursday January at your office in Houston At this meeting we can discuss mPowers capabilities to model grain yields using localized weather information and how this will fit your needs for your trading group I look forward to meeting with you If you have any questions prior to our meeting please let me know Thank you Bill Bodine mPower Specialist
